{"tid":1381621,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"千其唔好忽略對小朋友嘅文宣! 好重要!","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:02:59.000Z","uid":132174,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1a8c09ca50b84ae5c9707c7862928fd851eaeaca","tid":1381621,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:35:00.000Z","msg":"話說琴日我夢遊完返到屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食飯嗰時我叫阿媽轉台去 RTHK 32  想留意住事情發展<br />\n點知我表弟一嚟就話「班人又出嚟搞事」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽到個下真係好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實班哥哥姐姐咁辛苦出嚟都係為咗你哋下一代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢老竇老母係嗰啲典型中年 新聞都懶得睇<br />\n學校更加唔使旨意會教 根本所有小學教科書出版社已經比中聯辦控制晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n於是我食完飯就搵咗佢傾計<br />\n青春期啲𡃁仔通常有啲反叛，唔鍾意聽大人講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過好在記得之前見過佢睇大J<br />\n於是我開咗大J元朗條片俾佢睇 <br />\n我問佢「如果班人係出嚟搞事，點解大J又要跟佢哋一齊食煙霧彈？背後嘅動機係咩？」<br />\n可能佢真係第一次見到示威者受嘅苦，佢開始喺度思考，再唔係串串共咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後我叫佢自己了解下，橫掂平時都咁鍾意睇大J，睇完之後得出咩結論都唔緊要，有咩唔明可以大家一齊討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港嘅教育制度(尤其係小學)淨係識得教小朋友要服從大人講嘅嘢，唔識得去獨立思考對錯<br />\n所以好多時小朋友會assume咗 政府就好似皇帝咁，市民係一定要服從。<br />\n都係果句，我哋做咁多嘢都係為咗下一代，成功與否，如果呢份精神延續唔到落去，就真係好可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以為人父母嘅不妨帶多啲仔女出嚟，講多啲比佢哋聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce32de520f3a365258dddcc8eb09ce9c4810542","tid":1381621,"uid":132174,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:36:32.000Z","msg":"強烈支持唔同界別嘅Youtuber 拍片講政治！ <br />\n俾啲唔鍾意睇新聞嘅人知道發生緊咩事！<br />\n你敢講，我哋敢推你上神枱<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447fcd6640fb9f9df89c515f6c601a055fa208eb","tid":1381621,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:37:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01cfc21987a934f081454096bf70968c6a9b24ef","tid":1381621,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"达狗荼毒咗幾多細佬"},{"pid":"7915e43a8af5112d9a0cd1f70e169811d4e3a78c","tid":1381621,"uid":52462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"要求小朋友教學書移除幫助我們的人入面嘅警察"},{"pid":"05dd3f91802ec747366034797242030ba38dcde3","tid":1381621,"uid":41245,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:50.000Z","msg":"其實大J真係好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢對小朋友影響力真係唔細<br />\n而且真係唔係咁多youtuber有佢地位唔驚封殺乜乜乜<br />\n好多都要靠拍大陸game先維到生<br />\n講都要偷偷地話「今日出唔到片」"},{"pid":"f24c8c0b5c4228624b5f4338b8d98a3fe0d51b3e","tid":1381621,"uid":132174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"01cfc21987a934f081454096bf70968c6a9b24ef","tid":1381621,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:01.000Z","msg":"达狗荼毒咗幾多細佬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:50.000Z","msg":"佢有佢班「兄弟」我哋有成班香港人!"},{"pid":"f96e44d7217e9c2661ebf824320b736bceca6b6c","tid":1381621,"uid":265019,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HFZS6nV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHFZS6nV.jpg&h=6f234829&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PUvGfgg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPUvGfgg.png&h=115ceab9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0f8670741b03fc0bce3e68db5a918d73d638c83","tid":1381621,"uid":132174,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7915e43a8af5112d9a0cd1f70e169811d4e3a78c","tid":1381621,"uid":52462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:39:26.000Z","msg":"要求小朋友教學書移除幫